Package: allocation
Type: Package
Title: Exact Optimal Allocation Algorithms for Stratified Sampling
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2018-04-19
Author: Andrew M. Raim, Tommy Wright
Maintainer: Andrew M. Raim <andrew.raim@census.gov>
Description: This package implement several exact methods for allocating optimal sample sizes when designing stratified samples. These methods are discussed in <doi:10.1080/00031305.2012.733679> and <doi:10.1016/j.spl.2017.04.026>.
